CommitTreeFilter
protected static class CommitTreeFilter.FilterWrapper
extends BaseTreeFilter

Class that wraps a TreeFilter in a BaseTreeFilter so that BaseTreeFilter.include(RevWalk, RevCommit, TreeWalk) can always be called from CommitTreeFilter.include(RevWalk, RevCommit)
